  "texts": [
    "From the scores, it is possible to observe that overall, the Information-Retrieval system has achieved high values for BERTScore, all above 0.6.",
    "The average value revolves around 0.8 for this case.",
    "The scores of UNIEVAL FACTUAL CONSISTENCY mostly confirm the BERTScore scores.",
    "However, some UNIEVAL scores have values below 0.6.",
    "The average of UNIEVAL FACTUAL CONSISTENCY is around 0.74."
